    "15_0": {
      "status": "resolved",
      "note": "No Email. Root cause: The vehicle's seller field stores raw email addresses (e.g. sales@rfdprint.com), but findUserEmailByName was doing a name→email lookup in the users table. An email string like \"sales@rfdprint.com\" never matched any first_name, so the recipient set was empty and nothing was sent. The one-line fix short-circuits the lookup when the value is already an email. The email is now working"
    },
